              <%= image_tag("placeholder.png", size: '100x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body-text col-md-10">
              <div>
                You can't take care of the environment without first taking care of yourself! Exercise has many
                physiological and mental benefits, which include reducing your risk of chronic disease and dementia,
                increasing productivity, and boosting your mood. That's why it's extremely important to schedule
                time to move your body, even if you have a lot on your plate! Work out for at least 20 min every
                day for this week - it can be anything, from yoga to running to lifting weights to simply
                walking after a meal.
              </div>

